; EXECUTABLE_BLOCK_START
M73 P0 R145
M201 X5000 Y5000 Z500 E5000
M203 X500 Y500 Z30 E100
M204 P5000 R2500 T5000 ; sets acceleration (P, T) and retract acceleration (R), mm/sec^2
